<br>
It will be assumed that if you make the post that you are the raid leader unless you designate someone in your post.<br>
<br>
A few things you need to include in the post are:<br>
<br>
Day<br>
Time<br>
Zone<br>
Levels<br>
Goal (is it for loot? grind? a particular item?)<br>
Loot distribution rules<br>
<br>
You might also want to include information about the zone or a link to the zone.<br>
<br>
Please also post if it's an open raid for our guild allies to be invited to.<br>
<br>
Once it's posted here an officer will add it to the calendar and the guild motd. :)<br>
<br>
P.S. the raid guide has been re-written and posted under the guild rules. <br>
